  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的数据流转图，核心是GradeSync这个成绩同步服务。它要和学生数据库、内容分发网络都有交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，GradeSync作为起点，先连到StudentDB获取学生信息，再连到ContentCDN拉取课程内容，是这样吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但这里有个关键点——GradeSync之后要进入一个决策点，判断同步是否成功。这个菱形节点很重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把GradeSync、StudentDB、ContentCDN用粗箭头连起来，然后在后面放一个决策菱形。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "决策点分出两条路。如果同步成功，走Yes分支，进入LMS门户，然后到课堂服务，再经过ContentCDN，最后回到LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，您说的是从LMS门户到课堂服务，再到ContentCDN，然后又回到LMS门户？这个循环我确认一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这里有个小循环：课堂服务需要从ContentCDN获取教学资源，然后LMS门户展示给学生。之后课堂服务还要再连一次，最后回到那个决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，Yes分支我画好了：决策点→LMS门户→课堂服务→ContentCDN→LMS门户→课堂服务→回到决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支就简单些，直接回到GradeSync重新尝试，然后再进入LMS门户结束流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "No分支：决策点→GradeSync→LMS门户。这样整个流程就闭环了。我检查一下箭头方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不对，我再看一下——决策点D应该有两个出口，Yes和No。但D的入口是谁？前面是ContentCDN吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "按您最初说的，GradeSync→StudentDB→ContentCDN→决策点D。但D的标签也是GradeSync，这会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，决策点D的标签应该是判断条件，比如'同步成功？'，而不是GradeSync。但节点ID可以保留。另外，No分支回到的GradeSync是重新触发，不是同一个实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，D保持ID但显示为判断逻辑。No分支的J节点也是GradeSync，表示重新同步的实例。我调整一下标签显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看Yes分支的末尾，课堂服务I之后回到D，这个闭环会不会让流程无限循环？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "确实，I→D形成回路。但D是决策点，如果这次判断为No就会走J→K退出。或者我们需要一个终止节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "按现有设计，K就是终点，LMS门户作为最终展示层。循环是业务需要的，可以多次尝试直到成功。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我确认所有连接：A→B→C→D，D分Yes到E→F→G→H→I→D，No到J→K。都用粗箭头表示强依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "G→H是ContentCDN回到LMS门户，这一步是资源加载完成后的回调吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，ContentCDN把课件资源推送给LMS门户，然后门户通知课堂服务准备就绪，所以是H→I→D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
